title: Storytelling - Bones (2009)
description:
Translated from a short review in swedish. Sorry about any bad grammar or spelling or so.


"Bones sweeps over me with a great mix of subtle guitarplay and electronic beats. When I listen my thoughts wander of to Ulrich Schnauss or Aphex Twin meets Mark Kozelek, but without the song. With partwise glitchy beats and intriguing melodies Storytelling creates a dreamlike soundscape that's both meditative and edgy."



Released on Vintervila Jan 28th
